    "body": "This would be a good first bug, so you're certainly welcome to have a go.\r\n\r\nI recommend creating a new `WaitForTurretAlignment` activity (refer to `Turn` for a reasonable example), which sets `Turreted.DesiredFacing` and then waits until it reaches the desired facing before continuing.  This should be added to the activity queue from the `Transform` activity's  `OnFirstRun` method."
